%e4%b8%8a%e6%9b%b4%e4%b8%80%2c3%2c20221012%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPHM,111,上更一,3,20221012,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"上更一","JNO":"3","JDATE":"20221012","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例等"}